data.description: The search is finally over! Check out this charming 2-bedroom property nestled in Sun City Active Adult Community. You're welcomed by a generously sized living/dining area showcasing neutral tile floor and designer color palette providing a serene ambiance throughout. The well-kept kitchen boasts a pantry, tile backsplash, matching built-in appliances, and wood cabinetry offering ample storage. Discover comfortable bedrooms featuring ceiling fans and closets for all your belongings. The harmonious backyard offers multiple patio areas and will be the perfect spot for entertaining or simply relaxing! Don't miss out on this one!
